- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The proposed method for load-flow analysis may involve the use of AI techniques for optimization and efficiency. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture): The paper discusses the distribution network, which is a type of network architecture. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms): The paper proposes a method based on linear data structure, which falls under the domain of data structures and algorithms. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The proposed method may involve software implementation and optimization, which falls under the domain of software engineering.
